description:
We are pleased to present 3/75 Australia Street, St Marys brought to you by award winning agent Vedant Agrawal.

This modern 3 bedroom townhouse in a small complex is situated in a prime location and conveniently located close to all amenities such as Queen Street shops, St Marys Train Station, St Marys Village, bus stops, schools and even the future airport metro.

This is ideal for someone looking for a first home/investment and a must to inspect!

WHAT WE LIKE ABOUT THIS PROPERTY:
- 3 spacious bedrooms including built-in robes
- Master bedroom with ensuite
- Modern kitchen with gas cooking and ample cupboard space
- Open plan lounge and dining area
- Ducted-conditioning and down-lights present
- Crimsafe screen installed downstairs for additional security
- Modern bathroom with full height ceiling tiles
- Automatic garage with an additional drive through car space
- Low maintenance courtyard with grass area ideal for families
- Only 8 years old and is as good as new!

For further information or if you would like to arrange an inspection, please contact Vedant Agrawal 0490 173 525.
